commit_messages_json:
feat(more-action): Optimize the display and interaction experience of more action buttons on mobile devices.

- Adjusted the rounded corner style of ActionListItem buttons on mobile devices.

- Corrected the margin and padding behavior of ActionListItem in hover and press states.

- Removed redundant code from the Popover component, simplifying animation and layout logic.

- Optimized the use of Sheets in the Popover component for better responsiveness to different screen sizes.

- Supports using SlideDrawer instead of Popover as the pop-up container for MoreActionButton on mobile devices.

- Added the useCloseAction hook to uniformly close the behavior of Popover and SlideDrawer.

- Adjusted the layout of MoreActionContent and its child components to adapt to landscape and portrait modes and different devices.

- Added the MobileDrawerUpdateReminder component for mobile app update notifications.

- Updated the "Discover New Version" text in the language files.

- Added drawer scene support to the logger.

feat(Prime): Optimize OneKey ID login process and multi-platform pop-up navigation support

- Added a MoreActionProvider wrapper to the MoreActionButton component to optimize context management.

- Replaced page navigation for Native devices with pop-up navigation for Non-Native devices in the useLoginOneKeyId hook, improving user experience consistency.

- Added Native page redirection logic to PrimeLoginEmailDialogV2 to replace pop-ups, achieving cross-platform consistency in the login process.

- Added support for PrimeLoginEmailPageV2 and PrimeLoginEmailCodePageV2 pages to Prime routes.

- Added the prime.enter_email field for internationalization, improving multi-language support.

- Corrected CAPTCHA error message text for more accurate error type expression.
